{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1920/comments/10463000.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:None..None?path=gazebo%2Fphysics%2FWorld.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1920/_/diff#comment-10463000"}}, "parent": {"id": 10437475, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1920/comments/10437475.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1920/_/diff#comment-10437475"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1920, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1920.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1920"}}, "title": "physics::Light and physics::LightState"}, "content": {"raw": "I'm working on this. The plan is to deprecate `~/light` and `~/factory` topics and create 3 new topics:\n\n* `~/factory/light` : Used to spawn lights, takes `msgs::Light`\n\n* `~/light/modify` : Used to modify lights (pose included), takes `msgs::Light`\n\n* `~/factory/sdf` : Keeps the old behaviour of `~/factory`, which is spawning anything from an SDF string, including lights.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I'm working on this. The plan is to deprecate <code>~/light</code> and <code>~/factory</code> topics and create 3 new topics:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>~/factory/light</code> : Used to spawn lights, takes <code>msgs::Light</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>~/light/modify</code> : Used to modify lights (pose included), takes <code>msgs::Light</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>~/factory/sdf</code> : Keeps the old behaviour of <code>~/factory</code>, which is spawning anything from an SDF string, including lights.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-10-02T17:36:24.567254+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa